{"word":"G3891 - παρανομέω - paranoméō - par-an-om-eh'-o - Contrary to law","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρανομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paranoméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-an-om-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Contrary to law</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நியாயப்பிரமாணத்திற்கு விரோதமாய் இரு"},{"paragraph":"to be a paranomos, to act contrary to law, to break the law"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3551 - νόμος - nómos - nom'-os/3551\">G3551</a>; to <i>be opposed to law</i>, that is, to <i>transgress:</i> - contrary to law.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1772/1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544/3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545/3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547/3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548/3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549/3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550/3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551/3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891/3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892/3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458/458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459/459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460/460\">G460</a>"}]}